title: MOS In The Club Vol 3 2011
description:
[img]MOS In The Club Vol 3 2011[/img]

Kicking etiquette to the curb, Ministry of Sound have donned their finest wares and freshest pumps in preparation for the biggest cue jump of 2011 -IN THE CLUB VOL. 3. Two discs of darkened dance floor debauchery mixed by two of the biggest names in dance music; local hero Mobin Master and UK heavyweight MYNC. Taking you straight to the forefront of what?s hot in club land, IN THE CLUB VOL. 3 breaks stretches licensed capacity to its limits, with 43 tracks jammed into almost 160 minutes of epic dance music. Taking the reins on the first disc is Mobin Master, a man who shows more love for dance music than any other man, person or being in club land. Following on from Mobin is one of the UK?s biggest names in club music MYNC. Bypassing customs, MYNC has brought some of the biggest hits straight from Europe to his disc, with tracks from Swedish House Mafia, PNAU, Avicii, TiÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â«sto & Hardwell, Wynter Gordon, Tonite Only, alongside an army of club anthems set to have you sweating into the early hours of the morning. So get up and get down, with Ministry of Sound IN THE CLUB VOL. 3.
